{"tid":1749441,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[實測] 選舉投訴 只求公平公正 合乎程序","createTime":"2019-11-24T03:44:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T11:41:16.000Z","uid":41622,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"411b0d0c68d5a69da9def81e402575661193f9d4","tid":1749441,"uid":41622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:44:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ygbftiB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FygbftiB.jpg&h=7ad55dba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">話說小弟投票時<br />\n班職員係撚咁放D廢老入票站先<br />\n後生就要喺出面排<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咁唔公平一定要打去投訴！</span><br />\n<br />\n請善用133打過去你選區嘅投訴電話<br />\n打到通為止<br />\n最好你有電話錄音<br />\n<br />\n有人聽先講你嘅<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>選區</strong></span><br />\n佢會同你對一對選站地址<br />\n<br />\n之後講發生咗咩事<br />\n例如放人優先投票, 掌心雷, 被投票等等<br />\n<br />\n之後佢會問你點稱呼<br />\n記住係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔需要提供</strong></span>嘅<br />\n<br />\n最後拎返一個<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">投訴編號</span></strong><br />\n咁就完成</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3i2ye3O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3i2ye3O.jpg&h=a6dd228e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>光復香港 時代革命</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"4210032f832d9137735f3d3947984a28fba4a2a2","tid":1749441,"uid":198590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:46:41.000Z","msg":"幫推！"},{"pid":"51da03695c551014a5d5881758c144f445121432","tid":1749441,"uid":41622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:46:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tXiQ1Lg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtXiQ1Lg.jpg&h=9c868850&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"26630a75233c0833213e564e3e00741b758bbd40","tid":1749441,"uid":294281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime